    {
        "url": "/quotes/michael_specter_634074",
        "quote": "Some people will deny anything that displeases or scares them: unusual pain in their chests, unwanted lumps beneath their skin, or the fact that humans share ancestry with apes are a few examples. Another is climate change.",
