    {
        "url": "/quotes/michael_specter_634078",
        "quote": "Most reputable scientists agree that climate change is real and that the effects are likely to be bad. But nobody can say for sure exactly what 'bad' means. The safest and most equitable way out of this horrific mess is simple: cut fossil-fuel emissions.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Michael Specter",
            "url": "/quotes/michael_specter_634078"
